[HEADER]
id: cellar
title: Musty Cellar

[CONTENT]
The cellar is dark and filled with barrels. In the corner, you see a small, rusty lockbox.

[OPTIONS]
open_box | Open the lockbox -> ./lockbox.level
open_box_empty | Open the lockbox -> ./interactions/lockbox_empty.level
go_back | Go back upstairs -> ./tavern.level

[DIRECTIVES]
input_mode: choice

[OPTION_CONDITIONS]
option=open_box requires_missing_value=gem_taken
option=open_box_empty requires_value=gem_taken:true